      <section>
        <p>As part of the ongoing Erasmus+ projects implemented at PPMG "Acad. Ivan Tsenov" — Vratsa, the school's Erasmus Team organized a dissemination seminar for teachers from schools across the Vratsa region. The event showcased the results and experience gained during the current projects and aimed to share practical outcomes with local educators.</p>

